title: Proposal to collaborate with BabySwap on BSC
body:
This proposal aims to allocate $20K worth of MM token in our treasury to BabySwap pool on BSC (https://home.babyswap.finance/pools) to allow $BABY holders to stake $BABY for $MM awards within 30 days.

The purpose is to attract more new users on BSC and increase exposure to BSC community for Mushrooms Finance. In return, BabySwap will enable $MM-$USDT LP farming in its farms (https://home.babyswap.finance/farms).

BabySwap is a promising AMM+NFT-featured DEX for newborn projects on BSC which provides a more fridendly trading experience and better project support. Currently the daily trading volume on BabySwap has surpassed $40M.

Please vote YES if you think this proposal would benefit Mushrooms growth.
choices: NO - not make sense to me
author: 0x43229759E12eFbe3e2A0fB0510B15e516d046442
